title: Yemenis and Syrians stuck on docks of Port Sudan feel as though war has followed them
description: Mayhem is unfolding on the docks of Port Sudan.

title: You have 24 hours to catch evacuation flight out of Sudan, deputy PM tells British nationals
description: British nationals in Sudan have 24 hours to catch a flight before they are stopped, the deputy prime minister has said.

title: 'No one is left': 19 killed in Russian missile strikes - as Ukraine 'nearly ready' to launch counteroffensive
description: Ukraine is "to a high percentage ready" to launch its counteroffensive against Russia, according to the country's defence minister.

title: Sudan conflict threatens supply of key fizzy drinks ingredient
description: The conflict in Sudan has left international consumer goods makers racing to shore up supplies of gum arabic - critical to the food, drinks and cosmetics industry.

title: 'Starvation cult' death toll rises to 103 as popular preacher arrested in Kenya
description: At least 103 deaths are now being linked to a suspected starvation cult as authorities continue to find bodies in Kenya.

title: Sudan ceasefire extended as remaining Britons told to head to airfield 'quickly'
description: A ceasefire in Sudan has been extended for three more days despite continuing reports of heavy fighting in the capital Khartoum and the western region of Darfur.
